init_text:
Is Listening to a Book Just as Good as Reading It?

Do you listen to audiobooks? What are the benefits, in your opinion, of listening instead of reading? Are there advantages to reading that cannot be gained by listening? Which method do you prefer? Why?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: People would gather together to listen to the storyteller, and the story itself would be interpreted and revised by the townspeople.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: However, it bothers me that audiobooks are so convenient.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: However, it bothers me that audiobooks are so convenient.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I suggest everyone try an audiobook at least once.
